The paper is about a large-scale object detection system, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The authors also mention handling sparsely verified classes, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or natural language processing (cs.CL) if the classes are related to text or speech.
